// {"id":1159,"subject":"化學","topic":"1. Planet Earth","type":"choice","text":"Which of the following can distinguish a sample of limestone powder from a sample of table salt? (1) adding water (2) performing a flame test (3) adding dilute hydrochloric acid","points":5,"options":["(1) and (2) only","(1) and (3) only","(2) and (3) only","(1), (2) and (3)"],"answerLetter":"D"},
// {"id":1160,"subject":"化學","topic":"1. Planet Earth","type":"choice","text":"A flame test conducted for a sample gives a brick-red flame. The sample may contain","points":5,"options":["chalk.","quartz.","graphite.","rock salt."],"answerLetter":"A"},
