// {"id":1220,"subject":"化學","topic":"3. Metals","type":"choice","text":"Which of the following statements concerning iron and magnesium is correct?","points":5,"options":["Iron is ductile but magnesium is not.","Iron corrodes less readily than magnesium.","The abundance of magnesium is higher than that of iron in the earth crust.","Both magnesium and iron can have more than one oxidation number in their oxides."],"answerLetter":"B"},
