// {"id":1224,"subject":"化學","topic":"5+11. Fossil Fuels, Carbon Compounds and Chemistry of Carbon Compounds","type":"choice","text":"Which of the following statements concerning alkenes is INCORRECT?","points":5,"options":["They can decolourise a solution of bromine.","They can decolourise red litmus solution.","They can decolourise acidified potassium permanganate solution.","They can be polymerised to form addition polymers."],"answerLetter":"B"},
